J-Jotaro! L-Look!

4
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:08,980
Watch out, Koichi! Don't go any closer!

5
00:00:10,260 --> 00:00:14,240
Hey, I told you to look over here.

6
00:00:25,920 --> 00:00:27,330
Is that his Stand?!

7
00:00:27,330 --> 00:00:28,670
J-Jotaro!

8
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:33,780
H-He's here! He's taking the jacket!

9
00:00:34,970 --> 00:00:36,390
Good grief.

10
00:00:36,390 --> 00:00:38,540
Who would've thought he'd
come to get his suit now?

11
00:00:40,990 --> 00:00:42,770
The jacket is evidence!

12
00:00:42,770 --> 00:00:43,640
Wait!

13
00:00:43,930 --> 00:00:45,600
Don't run after it without thinking.

14
00:00:51,210 --> 00:00:52,790
Something about that Stand...

15
00:00:56,450 --> 00:00:58,070
is dangerous!

